 central thesis of the Lord's supper is that Jesus' own self-sacrifice, laying down his life for sin and offering salvation and forgiveness for those who believe.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The central thesis\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lord's supper\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"sin\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"salvation\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His body and blood broken for us.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His body\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our response should be to boldly, but compassionately share the good news of the gospel to those who are hungry for meaning and transcendence, who seek to worship in less satisfying gods.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our response\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"the good news\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"the gospel\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"meaning\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"transcendence\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"less satisfying gods\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amazingly, Jesus' death, burial, and resurrection offer forgiveness even for those who mock him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 5.666145385741099e-13, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/