ness Foundation\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic organizers of the Last Supper spectacle during the Opening Ceremony are so far behind the curve when it comes to diversity, equity and inclusion (DEI), what they were purportedly trying to promote.\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 4179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3992}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper spectacle\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"the curve\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4077}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"equity\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4112}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4126}, {\"ngram\": \"DEI\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest data show a significant surge in Fortune 500 companies including religion as part of their DEI initiatives, which helps them avoid such offensive and COSTLY mistakes.\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest data\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant surge\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"Fortune 500 companies\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"their DEI initiatives\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"such offensive and COSTLY mistakes\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, the world's biggest companies are embracing religiously inclusive workplaces at a faster pace than ever before, according to the 2024 Corporate Religious Equity, Diversity & Inclusion (REDI) Index and Monitor, released by the Religious Freedom & Business Foundation (RFBF) in May,\\\" he told Fox News Digital in an email.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4551, \"en